title: Hour 2 - Matt Buschmann & Sara Walsh
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Matt Buschmann & Sara Walsh
description:
Dan talks to Blue Jays Bullpen Coach, Matt Buschmann and his wife Sara Walsh about catching Aaron Judge's 61st homerun and why he didn't hold out for monetary compensation before returning the ball.
